<p>Dear Admin,</p>
<p>This is to notify you that a user has successfully logged into the system.</p>
<table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-bottom: 1rem; background-color: transparent;">
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th colspan="2" style="text-align: center; background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 0.75rem; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #dee2e6;">User Details</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr>
      <th style="padding: 0.75rem; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #dee2e6;">Employee ID</th>
      <td style="color: #28a745; padding: 0.75rem; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #dee2e6;">{{employeeId}}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <th style="padding: 0.75rem; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #dee2e6;">Name</th>
      <td style="color: #17a2b8; padding: 0.75rem; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #dee2e6;">{{firstName}} {{lastName}}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <th style="padding: 0.75rem; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #dee2e6;">Login Time</th>
      <td style="color: #ffc107; padding: 0.75rem; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #dee2e6;">{{loginTime}}</td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<p>If you have any concerns, please review the login logs or contact the user directly.</p>
